<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: MATTHEWS STUDIO EQUIPMENT POSTS PROFIT OF $456,000 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Matthews Studio Equipment Group in Burbank said its fiscal 1990 profit more 
than tripled from the previous year, to $456,000 from $138,000. 
</P>
<P>
Matthews, a provider of equipment and services to the film and television 
industries, said the higher earnings came on a 36% jump in revenue, to $20 
million in the year ended Sept. 30 from $14.7 million. 
</P>
<P>
The company said most of the profit gain stemmed from the expansion of its 
Hollywood Rental Co. unit, which rents production equipment to the studios. 
</P>
