</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Acqua Group, a Van Nuys producer of bottle-less water coolers, announced that 
it hopes to raise $3 million through an initial offering of 500,000 units 
consisting of 1 million shares of common stock and 500,000 warrants to purchase 
additional shares. 
</P>
<P>
