<HEADLINE>
<P>
IS IT JUST MUZAK OR MUSICAL MIND CONTROL? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
If the purpose of Muzak ("Humming Right Along," Dec. 19) is to "reduce stress 
and increase job efficiency," then why do I feel like killing somebody after 
being exposed to it for a few minutes? 
</P>
<P>
Face it. The whole idea behind Muzak is nothing but thought control. It's a 
wonder that Hitler or Stalin never thought of it. 
</P>
<P>
As for me, I would just as soon hear the ear-shattering garble from some 
idiot's boom box. 
</P>
<P>
FRANK. G. WILLIAMS, Independence, Calif. 
</P>
