Ambrose Baer, left, Justin Ramos, Gregory Dick. Front: Eric Muth, left, Romy 
Kirchhoefer. ; Photo, The 35-acre grounds of St. Michael's are covered with 
trees and shrubs that are planted and tended by the priests and seminarians. ; 
Photo, Father Phillip Smith leads choir practice. Seminarians may not know how 
to read music "but we give them plenty of experience," he says. ; Photo, COLOR, 
