<P>
Photo, Jim Harbaugh joined a lengthy list of injured quarterbacks when he 
suffered a separated shoulder on Dec. 16 against the Lions. ; Photo, Peter Tom 
Willis is the Chicago newcomer and is spending time on the bench, much as he 
did for four seasons at Florida State. Associated Press; Photo, In Harbaugh's 
absence, Mike Tomczak is the probable Bear starter for the playoffs. United 
Press International 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
