*Best director: Teri Ralston ("Quilters"). Runner-up: Des McAnuff ("A Funny 
Thing Happened on the Way to the Forum," La Jolla Playhouse/OCPAC). 
</P>
<P>
*Best actor: John Schuck ("Annie," California Music Theatre/OCPAC). Runners-up: 
Ernie Sabella ("Forum"), Ron Raines ("Showboat"). 
</P>
