*Best actress: Gretchen Wyler ("Annie"). Runner-up: Patti Cohenour 
("Showboat"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best featured actor: Eddie Bracken ("Showboat"). Runners-up: Gary Sandy ("She 
Loves Me"), Michel Warren Bell ("Showboat"), Sean McDermott and Ron De Vito 
("Starlight Express"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best featured actress: Consuelo Hill ("Showboat"). Runners-up: Laura Pryzgoda 
and Tricia Griffin ("Quilters"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best featured actor, revue: Tom Haffner ("Jacques Brel Is Alive and Well and 
Living in Paris," Backstage Theatre). 
</P>
<P>
*Best featured actress, revue: Myrona Delaney ("Side by Side by Sondheim," 
Saddleback College's Cabaret Theatre). 
</P>
<P>
*Best scenic design: Jacquie Moffett and Doug Williamson ("Quilters"). 
Runner-up: Douglas-Scott Goheen ("Into the Woods," UCI). 
</P>
<P>
*Best costume design: Molly Maginnis ("Showboat"). Runner-up: John Napier 
("Starlight Express"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best lighting design: Rick Belzer and Ted Mather ("Starlight Express"). Brenda 
Berry ("Forum"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best musical direction: Mark Turnbull ("Quilters"). Runner-up: Jim Coleman 
("Showboat"), Paul Bogaevi ("Starlight Express"). 
</P>
<P>
*Best musical direction, revue: Terence Alaric ("Side by Side by Sondheim"). 
</P>
